# nvidia-all patch list
#
# Columns (space-separated):
#   type      open | dkms | closed | any
#   file      path relative to nvidia-all-patches/
#   kmin      min kernel version, - = any
#   kmax      max kernel version, - = any
#   dmin      min driver version, - = any
#   dmax      max driver version, - = any
#   strip     patch -pN strip level (usually 1)
#   target    subdir for patch -d:
#               .            driver root
#               kernel-open  <open-src>/kernel-open/
#               kernel-dkms  <pkg>/kernel-dkms/
#   [flag]    optional: customization.cfg var, applied only when set to "true"
#   [excl_dver] optional: exact driver version to skip despite dmin/dmax range
#
# kmin/kmax = - : static (kernel-independent).
# Versions compared with vercmp.
#
# To add: drop file into all/ or <series>/, add line below.

# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# TYPE     FILE                                                                       KMIN     KMAX     DMIN         DMAX         STRIP   TARGET        [FLAG]                      [EXCL_DVER]


